Process Flow Documentation


->->-> End-to-End Booking Workflow <-<-<-

User opens app 

System fetches GPS location

Nearby bikes displayed

User selects bike & confirms booking

Vendor receives request

Vendor accepts

User tracks ride

Ride completes

Payment processed

Rating submitted

Admin monitors via dashboard


->->-> Admin Operational Flow <-<-<-

Manage user accounts

Verify vendor documentation

Resolve disputes

Generate reports


->->-> Vendor Operational Flow <-<-<-

Set availability (online/offline)

Accept/complete rides

Track daily earnings

Maintain bike status
